<br />\n最後就只有收左錢果幾十個出去<br />\n諗住帶動其餘藍屍<br />\n<br />\n最好辦法係分化佢地<br />\n用有人收錢做野來分化<br />\n或者有人收錢多d<br />\n因為藍屍相信只有收左錢先會做野"},{"pid":"01667671daff6c38b5aad750f49033e626526642","tid":1725751,"uid":260169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2f9ff1796a47b044b489698fa1c0247f555ddfb","tid":1725751,"uid":332503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:24:57.000Z","msg":"廢老只會叫人出去<br />\n自己唔會落手<br />\n最後就只有收左錢果幾十個出去<br />\n諗住帶動其餘藍屍<br />\n<br />\n最好辦法係分化佢地<br />\n用有人收錢做野來分化<br />\n或者有人收錢多d<br />\n因為藍屍相信只有收左錢先會做野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:45:12.000Z","msg":"分錢不均哩個係藍屍死穴<br />\n大家都係出咁多力，甚至冇出力個個都同我一樣人工<br />\n不公平。<br />\n可以幫佢睇整d文宣宣傳<br />\n藍屍打工攻略<br />\n拎錢排頭，開工行後。"},{"pid":"08b7782b0d0dac9a61efe358f1a63be4389c4af8","tid":1725751,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"浩召？"},{"pid":"9e619b86268498733082cac593e41d5293674e84","tid":1725751,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"啲語病多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1cd5cec6cb097fd99859458aaac0f989263efe","tid":1725751,"uid":302248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:47:42.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n成班錫身嘅垃圾藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004ca5f9f8fbf83195fc7c273eb77ae4249de312","tid":1725751,"uid":78515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:48:11.000Z","msg":"藍絲:一個幾錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自發 不了"},{"pid":"e17304ae3f13f17a4b4b1d6672d544d7f4d2af8c","tid":1725751,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"我退一萬步講<br />\n當佢地真係咁好打一個打幾十個<br />\n唔通全日全個月真係成隊守住條路咩<br />\n打遊擊一樣搞得死交通<br />\